      ** ======
      *
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      *
      ** Warning fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    WFldNmXAr
     C                   PARM                    WMsgIDxAr
     C                   PARM                    WMsgDtXAr
      *
      ** Securities screen 2 error indicators
     C                   PARM                    SEESEC2
      *
      ** Securities for file update - file format
     C                   PARM                    NwSEFilFmt
